title: Star Wars: Essence of the Force
description:
Essence of the Force	(2002),	480x264,	0:08:02

A group of marauders have assaulted the peaceful planet Doozadu, enabling their leader, the evil Mewey Maul and his band of mercenaries to seek the planets most prized possesion, the very essence of the Force. They have done this knowing full well that this treasure is under the protection of the Jedi order
